<h4>
 
**Whats is this?**
<h5>
A huge refinery, controlled by circuit to crack oils to try to maintain a storage of 80k-90k Petroleum Gas, 90k Light Oil, 90k Heavy Oil.

* 36x Advanced Oil Refinary
* 96x Plastic Chemical Plant
* 48x Rocket Fuel Chemical Plant
* 40x Battery Chemical Plant
* 13x Lubricant Chemical Plant
* 12x Sulfuric Acid Chemical Plant
* 24x Sulfur Chemical Plant
* 02x Flamethrower Chemical Plant
* 02x Explosives Chemical Plant
* 01x Empty Barrel Assembling
* 01x Fill Sulfuric Acid Barrel Assembling
* 01x Fill Water Barrel Assembling
* 01x Fill Lubricant Barrel Assembling
* 01x Fill Petroleum Barrel Assembling
* 01x Fill Light Oil Barrel Assembling
* 01x Fill Heavy Oil Barrel Assembling
___
<h4>

**Notes**
<h5>

**Power and Monitor** Use this Substation to power on and to output monitor signal.

Green signal for inside Refinary Storage  and Red signal for average itens per minute output.

![Power and Monitor](https://i.imgur.com/jgvFLEr.png)
___
**Fluids Storage**

![Fluids Storage](https://i.imgur.com/qhlt3Lj.png)

___
<h4>

**Versions:**
<h5>

* 10 - Minor fixes for v0.17 final + Extra Module for more Petroleum Oil production
* 09 - Minor fixes and add Sulfur production line to attend the new Blue Science recipe.
* 08 - Update to v0.17.60 (New Rocket Fuel and Flamethrower Recipes).
* 07 - Minor fixes. Add a New Crude Oil and Water connect.
* 06 - Now with input inserters to help in game (QOL)
* 05 - Minor fixes and a Solid Fuel output belt for new Blue Science.
* 04 - Now have a minute output count for Plastic, rocket fuel and Battery. And minor fixes.
* 03 - Fix Sulfur Production, Fix some electric poles and some little adjusts.
* 02 - Fix some problems and add Fill Barrels (Sulfuric Acid, Water, Lubricant, Petroleum Gas, Light Oil and Heavy Oil)
* 01 - First one
___
